GENEVA , September 2 -LRB- Xinhua -RRB- -- The International Olympic Committee -LRB- IOC -RRB- Tuesday suspended Ecuador from the Olympic movement .
The IOC is not satisfied with the way Ecuador is running its National Olympic Committee -LRB- NOC -RRB- .
The IOC had talked with the country 's IOC member Agustin Arroyo and announced the suspension .
The IOC said in a statement that it was `` in the best interest of the Ecuadorian sport movement and its athletes in particular . ''
The decision will not stop athletes from Ecuador taking part in international events at the moment .
But it may prevent the country having a say in the running of international sport and could affect the IOC funding they receive .
